Input- 
Book that can have AN author from existing author lists
Author which can have as many books as they want, title, ISBN

Process

Give the user a choice to do what they want 

Prompt the user to enter a book
accept book from the user 
store the book 

Prompt the user to enter an Author
Accept the Author 
store the author 

Prompt the user to  add a book to an author
accept book from the user 
store the book 

List all authors and books they wrote 

 


  
